name: 布雷林·兰金斯
name_full: 布雷林·兰金斯 Braelyn Rankins

last_movies.title: 末日巡逻队 第一季

introduction: Fun-loving actor, writer, and singing sensation, Braelyn Thomas Rankins celebrates a birthday in March and was born into a very creative family. Braelyn was born in Cleveland, Ohio and resides in Atlanta, Georgia. Braelyn's Mom recognized he was anointed early on and discovered him when he began ministering and singing at the tender age of 5. He enjoys writing movie scripts, video editing, swimming, and playing with friends.
